    the <a href="https://www.aaup.org/">American Association of
      University Professors</a> (AAUP) meets regularly to discuss
    campus affairs relevant to
    <a href="https://www.aaup.org/our-work/protecting-academic-freedom">
      academic freedom</a>,
    <a href="https://www.aaup.org/our-programs/shared-governance">shared
      governance</a>, and other
    <a href="https://www.aaup.org/issues-higher-education">issues of concern
    </a> to higher education
    workers.
  </p>
</section>
